<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/nav') %>
    <main>
      <section class="page-hero">
        <div class="container narrow">
          <p class="eyebrow">Services</p>
          <h1>How we help your business</h1>
          <p class="lead">
            TAIG offers a focused set of services designed to meet you where you are —
            whether you need reliable day-to-day support or strategic guidance for a bigger change.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="service-list">
            <article class="service-card" id="it-support">
              <div class="service-card-header">
                <h2>IT Support</h2>
              </div>
              <p>
                Keep your systems running and your team productive. We provide responsive technical
                support for the issues that disrupt daily operations — troubleshooting, maintenance,
                and practical fixes that get people back to work quickly.
              </p>
            </article>

            <article class="service-card" id="technology-consulting">
              <div class="service-card-header">
                <h2>Technology Consulting</h2>
              </div>
              <p>
                Navigate technology decisions with an experienced partner at your side. We help you
                evaluate options, plan implementations, and align investments with business priorities
                — so you choose solutions that fit, not just ones that are popular.
              </p>
            </article>

            <article class="service-card" id="operational-assessments">
              <div class="service-card-header">
                <h2>Operational Assessments</h2>
              </div>
              <p>
                Understand how your technology and processes work together today. Our assessments
                identify gaps, risks, and opportunities across your operations — giving you a clear
                baseline before you commit time or budget to change.
              </p>
            </article>

            <article class="service-card" id="problem-discovery">
              <div class="service-card-header">
                <h2>Problem Discovery</h2>
              </div>
              <p>
                When something isn't working but the cause isn't obvious, we dig in. Through structured
                discovery conversations and analysis, we help separate symptoms from root causes so
                you address the right problem the first time.
              </p>
            </article>

            <article class="service-card" id="business-advisory">
              <div class="service-card-header">
                <h2>Business Advisory</h2>
              </div>
              <p>
                Get strategic guidance that connects technology to business outcomes. We advise on
                priorities, trade-offs, and roadmaps — helping leadership make informed decisions
                about where to invest, what to defer, and how to measure progress.
              </p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section section-alt">
        <div class="container narrow">
          <h2>Not sure where to start?</h2>
          <p>
            Many clients begin with a conversation. Tell us what's on your mind and we'll help
            you identify the right entry point — no obligation, no pressure.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Start a Conversation</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
